description.narrative: UNICEF supported the Government to turn commitment into reality for children through the implementation of the National Plan of Action on Justice for children system reform for 2017-2021. The monitoring framework with specific targets and indicators to assess the progress showed the implementation at 60% by end 2019. Diversion of minor offenders from formal justice processes piloted by UNICEF was positively assessed by the Inter-Agency working group and recommended for scale-up. | Status:Constrained | As-of Date:16/12/2019
